            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I was a telemarketer (both in and outbound) for several years.  And I started off with how much you made Necosi like 8 bucks an hour but after about 6 Months I was making about 10 bucks then after a year around 12-15.  Plus commission.<br />
<br />
So there is definatly a good payrate and rightly so I hated that fucking job.  There was nothing worse then to go to work at 7 or 8 am on saturday and have to start calling people.  Half the people weren't even awake!<br />
<br />
As for the DNC list DEFINATLY tell them that.  And DON'T just call them names and hang up Say Can you please remove me from all your lists (remember to say ALL or they may just remove you from 1 list).  Then make sure you get confirmation... IE they say OK you are removed and they give you the whole it will be 6-8 weeks etc etc crap.<br />
<br />
When I worked as a telemarketer I loved DNC peeps they were usually the nice ones (the assholes always cursed you out and hung up guess what asshole your getting another call!).  And if you get all the peeps on the list on the DNC list your lines would go dry and you would get to wait for another list (Meaning we got to just sit on our asses and talk with friends do homework or generally just f**k around and NOT work until a new list was in which could take 30 min to an hour).</font></p>
             
